               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary”
 I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah and hymns
                     (fols. 5ra-8rb)
 I-2) Introductory exhortation (fols. 8rb-9rb)
 I-3)
                     ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... "I worship Thee..." (fols. 9rb-9vb)
 I-4)
                     Taʾammǝra Māryām: 81 miracles (fols. 10ra-85ra)
 I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾsi... “Does
                     not the man…” (distributed among the Miracles of Mary, fols.
                     11va-35ra)</summary>
